nd Exchanges do not make any representation or warranty that ASLs Mobile Trading service will be available at all times without any interruption and further that ASL shall not be responsible for any variation, reduction or imposition of the terms or the Clients inability to route any order through Mobile Trading facility.</li>\r\n<li>I/We agree that I/We shall not have any claim against the Exchange or ASL on account of any suspension, interruption, non-availability or malfunctioning of the System or Service or the Exchanges service or systems or non-execution of the orders due to any link/mobile/system failure at the Client/ASL/Exchange end for any reason thereof.</li>\r\n<li>I/We agree that I/We shall be liable and responsible for all legal compliance and adherence of all commercial terms and conditions in respect of the mobile connection/SIM card/mobile phone and ASL does not accept/ acknowledge any responsibility in this regard.</li>\r\n<li>I/We further agree that ASL shall not, directly or indirectly, be liable, in any way for security or the origin of the IP address used for trading by using the Mobile. I/We shall always be ready/prepared to utilize an alternative system to trade in case of any unexpected failures.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','',1,14,'2015-12-03 07:14:23',601,'','2015-12-03 07:20:54',601,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2015-12-03 07:14:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_paren