s=\\\"terms-gap\\\">Note: Paragraphs Two (2) and Five 5(d) do not apply to Guests (as defined below).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"terms-gap\\\">This Access Agreement (\\\"Agreement\\\") is between you and Axis Securities Limited (Axis Securities). The Services being provided herein relates to certain electronic services and information (\\\"Services\\\") to which you will have electronic access depending upon your user category through Axis Securities client web site (the \\\"Site\\\"):<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"terms-gap terms-1\\\">\\r\\n<li>If you are Axis Securities registered client, this Agreement is in addition to, and does not nullify, any other agreement, including the Member Client Agreement(s) and any annexure and supplements thereto between you and Axis Securities governing the conduct of your relationship with Axis Securities. The terms and conditions contained herein are in addition to and are to be read in conjunction with the terms and conditions as agreed under the Member Client Agreement(s) and any annexure and supplements thereto.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The terms and conditions contained herein may be amended, altered, supplemented, revoked, rescinded or replaced by Axis Securities, whether in full or in part, from time to time as may be notified on the Site or in such other manner as Axis Securities may deem fit.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You acknowledge that the information on this Site does not constitute an offer to sell or a solicitation of an offer to buy any security that may be referenced in the Site. If you wish to learn more about information contained on the Site, you may contact a representative of Axis Securities.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>To become a Registered Client you must indicate that you agree to be bound by all of the terms of this Agreement by clicking the \\\"I Accept\\\" button at the end of this Agreement. Until you click on the \\\"I Accept\\\" button below, you have no right to access any restricted area on the Site. A Guest will be deemed to accept the terms and conditions of this Agreement by using the Site.\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"terms-1sub\\\">\\r\\n<li>Guests: Users in this category will be provided with limited samples of Services offered on the Site but need not register to obtain access to the Site. For purposes of this Agreement, access by a Guest to the Site is at the sole discretion of Axis Securities, from time to time, may or may not permit a Guest to access the Site.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Registered Clients: This category of user will be provided with electronic access to the various Services provided by Axis Securities on the Site. The clients registered with Axis Securities (Registered Client) will have no time limitation with respect to the use of these Services as long as they remain a client of Axis Securities. Registration by submitting a physical application form and other documentary proof is required for this user category.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"conditionsist\\\">\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"terms-2 terms-main-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"terms-mian-hea\\\">SERVICES PROVIDED<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"term-2 terms-sub-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>Axis Securities shall provide you with electronic access, through your computer or other electronic device (collectively \\\"Computer\\\"), to the Services, including but not limited to the provision of information with respect to stocks and investments (\\\"Information\\\") and offering of online investment services in permitted securities, contracts and other instruments (\\\"Online Investment\\\") traded on the Bombay Stock Exchange Limited and the National Stock Exchange of India Limited (collectively \\\"Exchanges\\\") through the Site by means of an order routing system which includes inter alia all activities pertaining to order management such as capturing of an order, validation, routing of the order to the Exchanges, order cancellation, order confirmation and other related activities (\\\"System\\\"), value added services including but not limited to stock watch, market watch, research reports, portfolio aggregators, stock statements and transaction summaries, through the services of an unaffiliated Internet service provider (the \\\"Provider\\\") by you and the ability to communicate electronically with Axis Securities (\\\"E-mail\\\"), depending upon which category of User you are. Axis Securities may at its sole and absolute discretion, cancel or change any or all the Services or registration instructions in any manner whatsoever at any time or introduce additional Services from time to time, upon printed or electronic notice. Your continued use of the Services following the posting or notice of any changes or introduction of new Services will constitute your acceptance, ratification and confirmation of such changes. You agree not to attempt to connect to the Site, to use the Services or to view any of the Information if you do not agree to the terms of this Agreement.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Axis Securities reserves the right to charge a Registered Client a separate service fee for using the Services to effect transactions above a certain stipulated number\\/threshold.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"terms-mian-hea\\\">USER CODES<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"term-2 terms-sub-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>As part of you the registration process the Registered Client will be entitled to a user identification comprising of any alphabetical\\/numerical combinations or an alphabetical and numerical combination (\\\"User Identification\\\") and to a password for the purpose of authentication (\\\"Password\\\") to access the Site, System and the Services, as the case may be. The Password may include second level and \\/ or transaction level passwords as well and would be required to meet such requirements as may be stipulated by the Exchanges and\\/or the Securities and Exchange Board of India (\\\"SEBI\\\") and\\/or any other authority and Axis Securities, from time to time.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The System itself generates the initial Password and the same will be intimated to the Registered Client. Axis Securities is not aware of such initial Password. The Registered User agrees and undertakes to immediately change his initial Password upon receipt thereof. The Registered Client is aware that subsequent Passwords are not known or available to Axis Securities. (The User Identification and Password, are hereinafter collectively referred to as \\\"User Codes\\\").<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The User Codes are for your personal use only. You are responsible for the confidentiality and secrecy of the User Codes, and agree not to provide them to any third party. You shall ensure that you are the only authorized user of the User Codes. You are solely responsible for all statements made, orders entered and transactions effected by any third party and acts or omissions that occur while your User Codes are being used, whether or not such third party was authorized so to do. Axis Securities shall be entitled to presume that any order or instructions entered or communicated using the User Codes is the Client\'s own order or instruction. Axis Securities is not responsible for any breach of security caused by your failure to maintain the confidentiality of your User Codes. You shall be fully responsible and liable for and will pay or reimburse Axis Securities on demand all costs, charges, damages and expenses incurred by Axis Securities as a consequence of access and\\/or use of your account, the Site, System or Services by any unauthorized third party with your User Codes. You agree to notify Axis Securities immediately in the event of loss or theft of any or all of your User Codes, or if you believe the confidentiality and secrecy of any or all of your User Codes has been compromised in any way, or in the event of your learning about a possible or actual unauthorized use of the Services, together with full details of such loss, theft or unauthorized use including the date of such loss, theft or unauthorized use and in the case of unauthorized use, the manner in which it was used and the transactions effected pursuant to such unauthorized use. Axis Securities reserves the right to revoke your User Codes at any time without prior notice.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>In any of the events specified above, you shall immediately change your Password. However, if you are unable to change your Password for reason of you having forgotten your Password or your Password having been unauthorizedly changed by some other person or for any other reason, then you shall immediately request Axis Securities in writing to discontinue your old Password; and thereupon Axis Securities shall cause it\'s Site\\/System to discontinue the use of your Password and the System shall generate a new password which shall be communicated to you.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Notwithstanding the foregoing, the current norms for your User Codes are set out as under (these norms are subject to such other norms as may be notified from time to time by Axis Securities under this clause pursuant to any modifications to statutory laws, Rules, Regulations, Bye laws, Circulars governing the same and to Axis Securities internal policy):\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"terms-three-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>You are required to change the Password after logging onto the Site\\/System for the first time.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You shall not be allowed to access the Site\\/System if the User Codes is entered erroneous on three consecutive occasions.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You are advised to change your Password on periodic intervals on continuous basis.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The Site\\/System shall not allow you to have the password changed to the same as the old Password.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You shall be given prior intimation of expiry of Passwords at the end of every [14] calender days. In the event the Password has expired, you can apply for the new one as per the mode prescribed by Axis Securities from time to time.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>As