er. And that such NRI\\/PIO is entitled to request and contract as above under the laws as applicable to him\\/her.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"terms-mian-hea\\\">Mobile Trading<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"term-2 terms-six-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>I\\/We am\\/are registered with Axis Securities Limited (ASL) as the client. I\\/We am\\/are interested for trading through Mobile with ASL.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>I\\/We understand that the terms and conditions published on www.axisdirect.in will be applicable to Mobile Trading also.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>I\\/We am\\/are made aware by ASL regarding all the possible attendant risks, responsibilities and liabilities associated with trading through Mobile in addition to the risks associated with Online trading.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>I\\/We understand that ASL shall send the Order\\/Trade confirmation details on our existing registered E-mail id registered with ASL.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>I\\/We agree that the information sent by ASL on my\\/our E-mail id would be deemed to be a valid delivery of such information by ASL.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>I\\/We understand that trading through Mobile, including sending instructions or messages and conducting transactions through it may carry extra risks and may not be as secure as using the service via internet trading, Further I\\/We understand that the instructions (including inputting password for Mobile Trading) sent to ASL and any message, information and confirmation received from ASL through Mobile Trading is subject to the risk of being read, interrupted, intercepted, or defrauded by third party or otherwise subject to manipulation by third party or involve delay in transmission. I\\/We agree that ASL shall not be responsible or liable to me\\/us or any third party for the consequences arising out of or in connection with using, accessing and conducting transactions through Mobile Trading.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>I\\/We am\\/are aware that as it may not be possible for ASL to give detailed information on the mobile and mi